@node Future "Future"


@{b}Future@{ub}


	Maybe add some more tag variables like HSPACE and VSPACE.


	Get rid of the dependance on Viewtek. I know that AREXX can read the
information from the picture file itself. I just wrote the script quickly using
Viewtek because it was easier and because I am still learning how to read file
info in AREXX. However, the Viewtek part of the script is the quickest part of
it so this may take a while to happen.

@endnode

